      <title>国际货币基金组织称欧盟新债务规则只有在政治支持下才能发挥作用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/new-eu-debt-rules-can-only-work-with-political-support-imf-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织表示，只有债务水平高企、预算赤字巨大的国家真正付出物质和政治努力理顺公共财政，欧盟新财政规则才会发挥作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/new-eu-debt-rules-can-only-work-with-political-support-imf-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 14:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院维持美国对外国企业收入征税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/supreme-court-upholds-2017-us-tax-on-foreign-business-income</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院维持了 2017 年对美国企业海外利润征税的判决，驳回了一项可能为企业节省数千亿美元的上诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/supreme-court-upholds-2017-us-tax-on-foreign-business-income</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 14:06:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国斥资 29 亿欧元订购坦克，加强军事扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/germany-bolsters-military-expansion-with-2-9-billion-tank-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国计划额外购买 105 辆豹 2 A8 主战坦克，这是执政联盟为应对俄罗斯全面入侵乌克兰而制定的数十亿欧元武装部队现代化计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/germany-bolsters-military-expansion-with-2-9-billion-tank-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 13:35:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非总统拉马福萨开始就新内阁进行磋商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/south-african-elections-ramaphosa-consults-on-new-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨同意与反对党组成广泛联盟后，开始就任命新内阁进行磋商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/south-african-elections-ramaphosa-consults-on-new-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 13:25:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保守党候选人对选举日期的押注受到调查，里希·苏纳克面临压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/rishi-sunak-under-pressure-as-bets-on-election-date-by-tory-candidates-probed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国保守党候选人被控在首相宣布英国大选日期前不久对大选日期进行押注，官方对此展开调查，里希·苏纳克的竞选活动面临新的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/rishi-sunak-under-pressure-as-bets-on-election-date-by-tory-candidates-probed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 12:50:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度拒绝向法国记者发放许可，打击新闻自由</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/india-denies-permit-to-french-reporter-in-blow-to-press-freedom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据称，印度拒绝续签一名法国记者的许可证，这使他成为今年第三位离开印度的记者，这被视为对印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪政府领导下的印度新闻自由的又一次打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/india-denies-permit-to-french-reporter-in-blow-to-press-freedom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 12:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚领导人放弃竞选后，吕特接任北约最高职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/rutte-clinches-nato-top-job-after-romanian-president-drops-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在罗马尼亚总统克劳斯·约翰尼斯宣布退出竞选后，荷兰首相马克·吕特获得北约成员国的一致支持，成为下一任北约秘书长。目前，罗马尼亚是唯一一位仍有竞争力的候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/rutte-clinches-nato-top-job-after-romanian-president-drops-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 11:42:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查发现三分之一的首席财务官认为美国大选将影响投资决策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/a-third-of-cfos-see-us-elections-impacting-investment-decisions-survey-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[货币政策、通胀和劳动力仍然是未来 12 个月财务主管最担心的问题，调查中近三分之一的高管表示，由于美国总统大选的不确定性，他们正在推迟、缩减或永久取消投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/a-third-of-cfos-see-us-elections-impacting-investment-decisions-survey-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙的反对者面临法国商界领袖的敌意</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/macron-s-opponents-face-hostility-from-french-business-chiefs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法国，争夺权力的极右翼和左翼政治力量面临着企业家的敌意，因为他们提出了相互竞争的愿景，且未对如何修复公共财政给出详细的说明。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/macron-s-opponents-face-hostility-from-french-business-chiefs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 11:05:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国希望重启与法国电力公司的电力合同谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/le-maire-wants-to-reopen-talks-with-edf-on-power-contracts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔表示，法国电力公司向高耗能行业提供的长期电力合同价格“不能令人满意”，如果法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的政府在即将到来的立法选举后继续执政，法国政府希望重启与这家国有公用事业公司的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/le-maire-wants-to-reopen-talks-with-edf-on-power-contracts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 10:23:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
